Promenade is a collaborative piece with 3 voices. 

To start:
* select a voice and click on its link
* execute the first block of code
* after it has loaded, execute the second block.
* click the keyboard icon above the code box

Once the code is running you can use the 'Z' row of keys to start playing the sequence, or change the sequence using the GUI.
